route.name: El Paseito Mixto Permanent 103K
route.description: Some fire roads, some pavement and locations never visited on other Permanents/Brevets. The total elevation as per GPS  closer to 5600ft

course_points.n:
START: Beach Hut Cafe parking lot - Crissy Field
San Francisco, CA
BEAR RIGHT bike path - continue on path under Golden Gate Bridge
@ traffic circle stay on Conzelman Rd - uphill
top of Hawk Hill start steep descend  - use caution
Stay on Conzelman Rd @ Rathbone Rd  -towards Point Bonita
DIRT @ traffic circle unsigned Mendell Rd - ride to the end of dirt road

INFO CONTROL - End of Mendell Rd
Answer question on Brevet card
ride back on Mendell Rd towards pavement
DIRT END SLIGHT LEFT Field Rd

INFO CONTROL - Battery Townsley
Answer question on Brevet card
DIRT BEGINS - go through gate at end of building to enter Miwok Trail

INFO CONTROL - Bobcat @ Alta Trail
Just before power lines.
Answer question on brevet card

BEAR LEFT IMMEDIATE RIGHT use sidewalk @ Marin Ave to enter the bike path
DO NOT MISS THE ENTRANCE!
use pedestrian crosswalk/light to Cross Shoreline Hwy onto wooden deck/bike path
bike path after soccer fields - towards bridge

INFO CONTROL:  Seminary @ Weatherly
Answer question on brevet card
@ Traffic circle, continue straight on Paradise Dr

INFO CONTROL: Romberg Tiburon Center
3150 Paradise Dr
Answer question on brevet card
Tiburon, CA
cross Tiburon Blvd onto bike path
SLIGHT RIGHT bike path - cross bridge
SLIGHT LEFT Greenwood Beach Rd (parking lot entrance)
DIRT Trail Head Gate  - gate has #3747 in black/yellow sign

Almost a U turn, trail dips and then up a little, toward Old Railroad Grade Trail
DO NOT GO RIGHT
Wooden shack  - water fountain, first aid kit and bike repair kit, please use only what you need
at intersection - wood logs nicely placed to make intersection
Old Railroad Grade Trail @ Gravity Card Rd
Old Railroad Grade @ Hoo Koo E Koo

INFO CONTROL: West Point Inn
water/restrooms @ Inn
Answer question on brevet card
SLIGHT LEFT Old Stage Rd - after picnic tables
BEAR RIGHT DIRT ENDS Easy Grade Rd

Panoramic Hwy
water, restrooms @ Pantoll Ranger Station
(SL) Gate 5 Rd - use cross walk to enter left hand turn lane
SLIGHT RIGHT East Rd - continue under Alexander

INFO CONTROL: Moore Rd Pier entrance 
Answer question on brevet card
parking lot towards Golden Gate Bridge
enter Golden Gate Bridge West sidewalk
SHARP RIGHT (SS) Marine Dr @ stop sign
DIRT gravel trail right after the Warming Hut picnic tables/building
join the main gravel trail - San Francisco Bay trail

FINISH CONTROL - Crissy Field Beach Hut Cafe parking lot
East Beach San Francisco, CA
